<!DOCTYPE HTML>
<html>
	<head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>TechMeetups - L'agenda des meetups du numérique à Montpellier</title>
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon-32x32.png" sizes="32x32">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon-16x16.png" sizes="16x16">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('build/styles.css') }}">
        <link rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" href="/montpellier.rss" title="Flux RSS des meetups de Montpellier">
        <link rel="alternate" type="application/atom+xml" href="/montpellier.atom" title="Flux Atom des meetups de Montpellier">
        <script>
          (function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i['GoogleAnalyticsObject']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){
          (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o),
          m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m)
          })(window,document,'script','https://www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js','ga');

          ga('create', 'UA-83859-4', 'auto');
          ga('send', 'pageview');
        </script>
    </head>
	<body>
    {% set current_route = app.request.attributes.get('_route') %}

		<a href="https://github.com/jeremyb/techmeetups">
			<img style="position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0; border: 0;" src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/a6677b08c955af8400f44c6298f40e7d19cc5b2d/68747470733a2f2f73332e616d617a6f6e6177732e636f6d2f6769746875622f726962626f6e732f666f726b6d655f72696768745f677261795f3664366436642e706e67" alt="Fork me on GitHub" data-canonical-src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/github/ribbons/forkme_right_gray_6d6d6d.png">
		</a>

        <header class="hero is-info {{ current_route == 'homepage' ? 'is-large' : 'is-medium' }}">
            <div class="hero-head">
                <nav class="navbar">
                    <div class="container">
                        <div class="navbar-menu">
                            <div class="navbar-end">
                                <a href="#newsletter" class="navbar-item">S'abonner à la newsletter</a>
                                <a href="#about" class="navbar-item">A propos</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </nav>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-body">
                <div class="container has-text-centered">
                    <h1 class="title"><a href="{{ path('homepage') }}">TechMeetups</a></h1>
                    <p class="subtitle">L'agenda des meetups du numérique à Montpellier.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-foot">
                <nav class="tabs is-centered is-boxed is-medium">
                    <ul>
                        <li{% if current_route == 'homepage' %} class="is-active"{% endif %}>
                            <a href="{{ path('homepage') }}">Prochains événements</a>
                        </li>
                        <li{% if current_route == 'groups' %} class="is-active"{% endif %}>
                            <a href="{{ path('groups') }}">Communautés</a>
                        </li>
                        <li{% if current_route == 'stats' %} class="is-active"{% endif %}>
                            <a href="{{ path('stats') }}">Statistiques</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </header>

        <section class="section">
            <div class="container">
                {% block main %}{% endblock %}
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer class="footer">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="columns">
                    <div id="about" class="column is-three-fifths">
                        <div class="content">
                            <h4 class="title is-4">A propos</h4>
                            <p>
                                L'objectif de ce site est de vous permettre de découvrir les différentes communautés et événements organisés à Montpellier.<br>
                                Et si vous les connaissez déjà, de ne plus rater les prochains grâce aux flux RSS/Atom et iCal.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Retrouvez les communautés Montpelliéraines sur Slack :
                                <span class="tags has-addons">
                                    <a href="https://bit.ly/comm-mtp" target="_blank" class="tag is-link">Communautés Montpellier</a>
                                    <a href="https://bit.ly/comm-mtp" target="_blank" class="tag is-dark"><i class="icomoon-slack"></i></a>
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Les événements de ce site proviennent de la plateforme <a href="https://www.meetup.com/" target="_blank">Meetup.com</a>.<br>
                                Si le vôtre est manquant, n'hésitez à créer une <a href="https://github.com/jeremyb/techmeetups/issues" target="_blank">issue sur Github</a>.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Crédit photo : <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/wolfgangstaudt/2377437375/" target="_blank">https://www.flickr.com/photos/wolfgangstaudt/2377437375/</a>.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="column">
                        <section class="content">
                            <div class="field is-grouped is-grouped-multiline">
                                <div class="control">
                                    <div class="tags has-addons">
                                        <a href="{{ url('feed_mtp', { _format: 'rss' }) }}" class="tag is-link">RSS</a>
                                        <a href="{{ url('feed_mtp', { _format: 'rss' }) }}" class="tag is-dark"><i class="icomoon-rss"></i></a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="control">
                                    <div class="tags has-addons">
                                        <a href="{{ url('feed_mtp', { _format: 'atom' }) }}" class="tag is-link">Atom</a>
                                        <a href="{{ url('feed_mtp', { _format: 'atom' }) }}" class="tag is-dark"><i class="icomoon-rss"></i></a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="control">
                                    <div class="tags has-addons">
                                        <a href="webcal:{{ url('ical_mtp', {}, true) }}" class="tag is-link">iCal</a>
                                        <a href="webcal:{{ url('ical_mtp', {}, true) }}" class="tag is-dark"><i class="icomoon-calendar"></i></a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="control">
                                    <div class="tags has-addons">
                                        <a href="https://github.com/jeremyb/techmeetups" class="tag is-link">techmeetups</a>
                                        <a href="https://github.com/jeremyb/techmeetups" class="tag is-dark"><i class="icomoon-github"></i></a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                        <br>
                        <section id="newsletter">
                            <h4 class="title is-4">S'abonner à la newsletter</h4>
                            <div id="mc_embed_signup">
                                <form action="//test.us7.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=0e9908af2ac6112997ebb96df&amp;id=77d16b689f" method="post" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" class="validate" target="_blank" novalidate>
                                    <label for="mce-EMAIL">
                                        Pour ne plus rater les prochains meetups de Montpellier,
                                        inscrivez-vous à la newsletter :
                                    </label>
                                    <div id="mc_embed_signup_scroll" class="row uniform 50%">
                                        <div class="field has-addons">
                                            <div class="mc-field-group control">
                                                <input type="email" value="" name="EMAIL" class="input required email" id="mce-EMAIL" placeholder="Email">
                                            </div>
                                            <div style="position: absolute; left: -5000px;" aria-hidden="true"><input type="text" name="b_0e9908af2ac6112997ebb96df_77d16b689f" tabindex="-1" value=""></div>
                                            <div class="control">
                                                <input type="submit" value="Je m'inscris !" name="subscribe" id="mc-embedded-subscribe" class="button is-info">
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div id="mce-responses" class="clear">
                                            <div class="response" id="mce-error-response" style="display:none"></div>
                                            <div class="response" id="mce-success-response" style="display:none"></div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </form>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>

        {% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}
	</body>
</html>
